      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "This car is an absolute dream and in truly pristine, showroom-quality condition! It has been meticulously cared for and looks as if it just rolled off the assembly line, offering a flawless driving experience and a stunning appearance inside and out. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one for you\u2014it's a rare find that's ready for its next proud owner!",
