      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptional vehicle, currently held in peerless, showroom condition. Meticulously preserved and mechanically absolute, this specimen represents the pinnacle of its class. An acquisition for the discerning driver who demands uncompromising quality and aesthetic perfection, this vehicle has undergone a rigorous inspection to ensure it meets our most exacting standards of excellence.",
