      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, preserved in showroom condition and representing the pinnacle of its class. The exterior maintains its original luster with no imperfections, while the interior remains entirely unblemished, reflecting a history of climate-controlled storage and fastidious maintenance. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, having undergone a comprehensive technical evaluation to ensure it meets our exacting standards of performance. This is an invitation for the discerning buyer to acquire a specimen of unparalleled quality and distinction.",
      "price": 43500.0,
